      "date": "2012-11-07 01:31:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nhm, so the problems run a bit more deeply than I imagined.\nWhile on my node cfsloc is as shown in my patch, on maloo cfs loc is actually a different value, not added with 0xffffff (example of how it did not work before too: https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_logs/2999ac42-174e-11e2-ad4e-52540035b04c/show_text )\n\nBack to the drawing board, I guess.\n\n\nThanks for looking into the results",
